To properly execute files:

./bufr_sfc2ob.x gdas.adpsfc.tHHz.YYYYMMDD.bufr YYYYMMDDHH
./bufr_ship2ob.x gdas.sfcshp.tHHz.YYYYMMDD.bufr YYYYMMDDHH

./runob2lit_imd_obs.x files.txt YYYYMMDDHH

To convert muliple files, place input BUFR data in bufrdecodeslr/bufrobs,
and edit and run the convert.sh script accordingly. Output data will be placed
in bufrdecodeslr/lrobs.
